  "text": "What is more interesting is that CS is not influenced by any of the variables from the group of personal and demographic characteristics. On the other hand, a connection between the variables of age and gender and CS were demonstrated in the automotive industry [CITATION_1] ), in services [CITATION_2] , and, finally, weakly in organic products (food industry), with the latter also including the variable of income [CITATION_3] .",
